platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 一場謀殺疑雲探案冒險

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Packed with great puzzles, humour, and voice acting–plus a thrilling murder mystery–this is everything you could want in a point-and-click adventure.
Packed with great puzzles, humor, and voice acting—plus a thrilling murder-mystery—Tangle Tower is everything you could want in a point-and-click adventure.
滿載精彩謎題、幽默笑料和配音，再加上驚心動魄的謀殺之謎，為你帶來理想中的點擊式冒險遊戲。
L’aventure pointer-et-cliquer idéale avec ses casse-têtes bien pensés, son humour et ses doublages — mais aussi un palpitant mystère meurtrier.
